</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 John Vaswani has been appointed vice president and general manager of 
Rockwell's North American Aircraft Modification division in Anaheim. He 
succeeds Gene P. Burbey, who retired after 12 years in various management 
positions for Rockwell Aerospace businesses.Before his new appointment, Vaswani 
was executive vice president of the division and, before that, vice president 
for international operations at Rockwell's former Defense Electronics business. 
</P>
<P>
 * John Houten has been appointed vice president and manager of construction 
lending in Orange County for California State Bank.  
</P>
<P>
 He was formerly vice president and regional manager for Commercial Center 
Bank. 
</P>
<P>
 * Larry Valenti has been appointed director of human resources for Pilkington 
Aerospace Inc. in Garden Grove. Before joining the manufacturer of aerospace 
transparencies, he was senior director of human resources for Pilkington Barnes 
Hind, a San Diego manufacturer of contact lenses. Valenti also spent nine years 
at Davis Walker Corp. as corporate vice president for human resources. 
</P>
