 * Nancy Mammorella has been appointed field marketing director for Coors 
Brewing Co.'s Irvine office, which is responsible for the management of Coors' 
sales and marketing efforts in Southern California, Las Vegas and Hawaii. She 
was previously brand manager and acting director for the Original Coors brand 
in Golden, Colo. In addition, Russell Frain was selected retail account 
director. He was formerly business development director for Pepsi-Cola in the 
Southern California area. 
</P>
