advertising and public relations agency. Getsey succeeds founder Chip Shafer, 
who becomes chairman. Getsey was previously director of marketing 
communications at CalComp, a Lockheed-owned supplier of computer graphics 
hardware in Anaheim. Before that, he was vice president and managing director 
of a Foote, Cone & Belding Communications subsidiary. 
