for America to enjoy a milder winter climate. 
</P>
<P>
 One day while looking out the window, Rudy commented to Olga that it was 
beginning to rain outside. Knowing her husband's eyesight was not what it once 
was, she asked, "Are you sure it's raining, dear?" He bellowed back: 
</P>
<P>
 "Rudolph the Red knows rain, dear." 
</P>
<P>
 -- John Carvaly 
