OCEAN VIEW'S JOHNSON WINS JUNIOR GOLF EVENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Robert Johnson of Ocean View shot a one-under-par 72 Thursday to win the 
junior class competition of the Junior Golf Winter Classic at Skylinks Golf 
Course in Long Beach. 
</P>
<P>
 Other Orange County golfers placing in the junior class were Huntington 
Beach's Perry Dickey III, who finished third (72); Ryan Olson of Dana Hills in 
fourth (73); Ryan Donovan of Esperanza in fifth (74) and Mike Bulsombut of 
Ocean View in eighth (75). 
</P>
<P>
 In the senior class division, Alex Yi of La Quinta and James Wooley of 
Valencia finished in a tie for third (72). 
</P>
<P>
 Kelly Craig of Santa Margarita High shot a 75 to take fourth in the sophomore 
competition. 
