two-month investigation of an incident at a McDonald's in Simi Valley and two 
incidents at a McDonald's and a Carl's Jr. in the San Fernando Valley. 
</P>
<P>
 Fellows is being held in Los Angeles County Jail in lieu of $300,000 bail. 
</P>
<P>
