8-year-old girl was standing at the sink in the women's restroom when a man 
came in, knelt by the girl and licked her leg, authorities said. The man then 
asked the girl for a kiss, but she refused and left, officials said. 
</P>
<P>
 Fellows was later identified as a suspect in that incident, police said. Simi 
police shared information they obtained in the case with the Los Angeles Police 
Department, which led to Fellows' arrest by the LAPD, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
 Fellows is also accused of molesting a 9-year-old girl in the women's restroom 
of a Carl's Jr. restaurant in the Valley, officials said.  
</P>
<P>
 He is also under investigation for a molestation involving a 4-year-old girl 
in Northridge. TRACY WILSON 
