<TEXT>
<P>
 Coonan Clinical Laboratories Inc.: The private Costa Mesa company said it has 
agreed to be acquired by ChemTrak Inc., a Sunnyvale manufacturer of disposable 
health tests, for up to 400,000 newly issued shares of ChemTrak common stock.  
</P>
<P>
 Stephen J. Coonan, founder and president, would become a vice president of 
ChemTrak and president of the Coonan Clinical Laboratories subsidiary. 
Operations of Coonan Clinical Laboratories, which is developing a home HIV-1 
blood collection kit, would be moved to ChemTrak's Sunnyvale facility. 
