Ft. Myers when the collision occurred. 
</P>
<P>
 Most passengers weren't aware of the collision until they left the plane, but 
a few said they heard a thud. 
</P>
<P>
 "You could hear something happen," Barbara Bowers said. "It was pretty scary." 
