 Subway tunneling -- In Wednesday's editions, The Times incorrectly reported 
the breakdown of the City Council's vote on whether to resume subway tunneling 
beneath Hollywood Boulevard. The vote was 10-2, with Councilmen Joel Wachs and 
Mike Hernandez dissenting. 
